<span id="freeTextContainer13619236978739654226">I loved 90% of the book. I was disappointed when it came to the final few chapters but to me mr.darcy stops being a gentlemen when he succumbs for his desire for Elizabeth before they are married. If you are looking for a clean romance, this isn&apos;t it in the last few chapters. If you took out the one scene of desire... it would have been perfect! but that ruined it for me.</span>
  <span id="freeText13619236978739654226" style="display:none">I loved 90% of the book. I was disappointed when it came to the final few chapters but to me mr.darcy stops being a gentlemen when he succumbs for his desire for Elizabeth before they are married. If you are looking for a clean romance, this isn't it in the last few chapters. If you took out the one scene of desire... it would have been perfect! but that ruined it for me.</span>
