<div id="review_3997338140" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3997338140" />
    <a title="Marie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/117010102-marie"><img alt="Marie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1600991392p2/117010102.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3997338140?book_show_action=true">May 14, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marie" href="/user/show/117010102-marie">Marie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/11355151-mr-darcy-and-the-secret-of-becoming-a-gentleman">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117010102-marie?shelf=jaff">jaff</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117010102-marie?shelf=2021">2021</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117010102-marie?shelf=owned">owned</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117010102-marie?shelf=mature">mature</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3997338140" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17061068791676446809"><strong>Excellent!</strong><br/>I know I joined the JAFF party late but I still don’t know how I didn’t see this book before now. A brilliantly-written story filled with page-turning dialogue that focuses almost entirely on Darcy and Elizabeth. Since my “purist” notions have evolved over time, I didn’t even mind the fall from propriety. Definitely recommend. Contains mature, but not overly graphic situations. I would love to see more from this author.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

